Package com.backEnd

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Config
    This class holds all of the constants that are used throughout the program.
    DiffExCalc
    This class executes the differential expression calculator.
    FileFilterer  
    FileParser
    This class is used to parse files found in gene expression analysis and convert large amounts of files into matrix form.
    Gene
    This class is used to store Genes.
    GenesList
    GenesList serves as a wrapper class for ArrayList.
    MetaDataParser
    This class is responsible for parsing the metadata files.
    StatusUpdate
    This class allows for transfer of print statements within threads.
    TSVtoCSV
    This class converts .tsv files into .csv files so that they are more usable for the R script
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FileFormatException
    This class is an exception thrown if the user has entered incorectly formatted metadata and/or data files.
